Package: biophybreak
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Outbreaks with Sequence and Biomarker Data
Version: 0.6.0
Date: 2021-10-20
Authors@R: c(person("Don", "Klinkenberg", 
    email = "don@xs4all.nl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	   person("Erik", "Lundgren",
    email = "elundgren@lanl.gov", role = "aut"))
Description: Implementation the outbreak analysis method described by 
    Klinkenberg et al (2017) <doi:10.1371/journal.pcbi.1005495>. 
    Simulate outbreaks, analyse datasets by creating samples from the 
    posterior distribution with a Markov-Chain Monte Carlo sampler, 
    and summarize the output. Modifications allow the use of individual specific
    non-parametric infection time distributions that can be obtained with biomarkers.
License: GPL (>=2)
